---
title: Crispy-Skin Chicken Breast with Mushroom Vin Sauce, Roasted Carrots & Garlic Mash
description: Inspired by a French classic, our crispy skin chicken breast is a recipe packed with rich, bold flavour. Chicken with a crispy and golden skin is drizzled in a glossy and thick vin sauce, made with mushrooms, shallots and red wine stock. Smooth, pillowy garlic mash and carrots roasted with a sprinkling of sugar to draw out their natural sweetness make the perfect sides.
